OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FItaly pays for tourists'   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdine and dash in Albania   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, In a unique act of diplomacy, Italy's  
OL,6, government has settled the restaurant  
OL,7, bill of four Italian tourists in       
OL,8, Albania who left without paying.       
OL,10,FThe dine and dash in the city of Berat 
OL,11,Fmade headlines in both countries.      
OL,13,FThe chatter prompted Albania's Prime   
OL,14,FMinister Edi Rama to raise it with his 
OL,15,FItalian counterpart, Giorgia Meloni,   
OL,16,Fwhile she was visiting the country.    
OL,18,FShe responded by telling her ambassador
OL,19,Fto "go and pay the bill for these      
OL,20,Fidiots," he told La Stampa newspaper.  
